<emphasis bold="true" box="[144,248,1316,1335]" pageId="6" pageNumber="1041">Figure 4.</emphasis>
A–E, 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[322,645,1315,1335]" pageId="6" pageNumber="1041">
<taxonomicName authority="Karaman &amp; Hammouti &amp; Pavićević &amp; Kiefer &amp; Horvatović &amp; Seitz, 2011" authorityName="Karaman &amp; Hammouti &amp; Pavićević &amp; Kiefer &amp; Horvatović &amp; Seitz" authorityYear="2011" box="[322,544,1315,1335]" class="Insecta" family="Rhaphidophoridae" genus="Troglophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="1041" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zorae" status="sp. nov.">
